  "_comment_gs1us_mapping": [
    "Cooling CTE per GS1 US 'EPCIS Recommendations for FSMA 204 CTEs' R2.0, §3.",
    "Modelled as THREE events because CBV has no dedicated 'cooling' bizStep:",
    "  1. receiving   — food arrives at the cooling facility from the farm.",
    "  2. other       — cooling process itself (CBV 'other' is explicitly allowed for operations",
    "                   not yet in CBV). EPCIS 2.0 sensorElementList carries the cooling temperature.",
    "  3. transporting — cooled food leaves for the immediate subsequent recipient.",
    "KDE mapping:",
    "  Farm-of-origin location: event 1 sourceList type=location.",
    "  Cooling location: readPoint on all three events + bizLocation on event 2.",
    "  Cooling date: event 1 / 2 eventTime.",
    "  Subsequent recipient: event 3 destinationList type=location.",
    "NO fsma: extension fields ride inside the event."
  ],
